snippet.title: Europa Universalis IV: Domination | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Prepare to write new stories of the world’s greatest empires in Europa Universalis IV: Domination. More historical flavor will bring you closer to the past as you struggle to hold on to the reins of power. Wishlist today, and claim a seat in the grand theatre of history.
